Downlaod the following extensions for visual studio:

Open visual studio
select option of "continue without code"
on top tool bar, click on "extensions"
a new window will pop up, select the "online" option
click on the search bar and find the following extensions
  "web essentials 2019"
  click on download
  "visual studio productivity power tool 2019"
  click on download
  "resharper"
  this one will say trial in the bottom left. If you have a jetbrains account, it will convert to the student adition. when you click download
  it will pop open your internet browser and then the "run/save/cancel" option for the file at the bottom of the screen. click run.
